        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Hi <a class="mention" href="https://community.frontity.org/u/mburridge">@mburridge</a> it’s a little difficult to share the actual code as it is for work, I will share code that is similar though.</p>
<p>I am styling the blog posts in the Post component like here: <a href="https://community.frontity.org/t/how-to-style-blog-page/587/9" class="inline-onebox">How to Style Blog Page?</a></p>
